Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Hammer-Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, stand up! This Duel ain't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you! Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never try to cheat again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, you no good bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough already, Gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our true job is to search for Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.38,0:00:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Droite's good spirit saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now disappear from Heartland City this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shitty bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:01:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was back during the opening ceremony of the World Duel Carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after separating from Yuma and the others, I hid here to analyze the other Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I ended up sleeping through the entire day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta start collecting Heart Pieces, or I ain't gonna make it into the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already the second day of the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than likely, only a ton of strong guys remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I should lose a Duel and lose this thing in the process, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought up a good plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! Now I've got four Heart Pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need one more to advance to the finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No biggie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least I get to Duel my way while he isn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Numbers... My memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what in the world am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Taichi! What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma! Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Tokunosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow, you're participating in the Duel Carnival, Taichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yup, and you better believe I'm after the championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's how you feel, I bet you gathered up a considerable amount of Heart Pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, not exactly... It's a bit pitiful, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You collected that many?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me see your Heart Piece for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's the big deal? Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a match!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be taking this Heart Piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In return, you can pick all the Heart Pieces you want from this bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Huh?!\N - Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're disqualified?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the Heart Pieces all have a specific pattern carved into their edges.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise they won't fit together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Heart Pieces he gave me were fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Candy?!\N - Candy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they were suspicious looking, so I licked them and this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, the edges are all stuck together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This happened because you tried to get Heart Pieces improperly, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a point, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you please help me look for Tokunosuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess there's no helping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It melted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kiddin' me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he trick me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the people in this place are so stupid they don't even realize the law that states there's a flip side to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to them, I was able to gather four Heart Pieces without having to Duel even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means if I choose one of the pieces from inside this bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can pass right to the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! Where the heck did that Tokunosuke go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.59,0:04:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's gathering Heart Pieces like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- If he's collected them, then...!\N - If he's collected them, then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I collected all the Heart Pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you already collected them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you in high spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean I'm the first one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yippee! I'm the first one to advance to the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to lick it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You talking about my Heart Pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Heart Pieces aren't made for licking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-And they're bound to be dirty after being in people's pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then should I grab your mouth and {\i1}make{\i0} you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lick it! I just need to lick it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It melted!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it melt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This is candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lying, thieving little cheapskate! Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are {\i1}those{\i0} supposed to be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:06:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wasn't me! I-I was tricked!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Leg'go!\N - Tokunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I get closer, I stretch my hand out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}towards that shining light leading towards tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I dream of a world that expands from my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't a clue of where things like dreams and hopes are at.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I run looking for it, I still can't seem to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I have fallen into a gap of truth and lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, our grand tale has yet to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:07:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's move on towards tomorrow, \Neven if our road begins to fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will jump forward, before all my\N strength completely drains.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The closer I get, the further it becomes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that truth that I must seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's to find hope that we desire from a future unseen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With a heart stronger than anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll learn to keep running up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the strength to win any battle, \Ndespite just how weak I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My purpose is to find,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with these invaluable friends of mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The future of the world expanding\N from my feet with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said to pipe down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I'm gonna start crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(454,496)}"Number 37: Disqualified from the W.D.C.!?\N Heartland's Assassins Droite and Gauche"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do with Tokunosuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That noisy little boy from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you what you plan to do with Tokunosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He fabricated Heart Pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As punishment, his deck will be confiscated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be disqualified and deprived of all future participation in the Duel Carnival for the rest of his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it so he can never Duel again before beating his ass right out of Heartland City!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang on a minute! You don't have to go that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That far"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This pest's dishonored Dueling!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot forgive him for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me! I'll give you my deck or whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that what Tokunosuke did may be unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's no reason for you to go this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is an issue between Duelists, let's settle it with a Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on taking Tokunosuke, Duel with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Duel, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting! But I'm strong, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, that's just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can both come at me at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel will be 2-on-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you Duel against the both of us and manage to defeat the both of us, it's your win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll forget about what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you end up losing, {\i1}you{\i0} will be required to take the punishment in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it? You on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Don't act like you've got the balls to fight when you're nothing but an incompetent Duelist not even worth talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I accept that Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you lose and they take your deck, you won't be able to continue participating in the Carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Astral's still not here, right? It's way to reckless for you to fight both of them by yourself, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I can't just abandon Tokunosuke, my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting! I'll test out that spirit of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! I won't let myself lose to the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Disk, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Gazer, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Disk, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}AR Vision - Link established.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. I can't remember anything past that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's that miracle that saved Yuma and I during the Duel with Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is the "Power of ZeXal"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma's starting a Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 96!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.83,0:12:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You broke the seal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was what we Numbers wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry up and finish this, Gauche.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral's not here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, this is so reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Yuma can beat those two on his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who do you think he's fighting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0}, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah! I'm good enough to handle these two on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a Monster in face-down Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then set a card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! All that talk and you go and play on the defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to lose this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the other Numbers giving you their strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you. It's what all the Numbers {\i1}want{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.85,0:13:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want the same! The destruction of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying I want to destroy the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you didn't, how can you explain my being here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Phantom Butterfly Assassin Morpho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then set two cards and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1200 Attack Points...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll regret the spirit you had to challenge us to a match!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Hammer-Rush Bouncer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can be Special Summoned from my hand when my field is empty while my opponent controls a Monster, Magic, or Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got 2300 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He Summoned a Level Six Monster right off the bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now come at us with everything you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My opponents have a Monster with 1200 Attack Power and another with 2300 Attack Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And in my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I decided which of you I'm gonna beat first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch my face-down Defense Mode Monster into face-up Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, Rai Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. It's got 1200 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can that piss-poor Monster possibly do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! Just you watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then Summon Tasuke Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! If I destroy Morpho with Tasuke Knight and then Direct Attack with Rai Rider, I'll deal her great damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:15:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Tasuke Knight! Attack Morpho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wave Pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Permanent Trap, Scales of Subordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When an opposing Monster declares an attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this card can change this card into an Equipment Card and change the target's Battle Position from Attack to Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tasuke Knight's attack was stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your spirit leads you to rush in and miscalculate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't win without Astral around after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't Astral come out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, remember your mission, Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Come to our side, Astral!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor - Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope, does this mean you've decided to stand against us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then! I'll just start by absorbing you first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Black Mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Phantom Butterfly Assassin Swallowtail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I activate the second effect of Scales of Subordination!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once per turn, I can change the Battle Position of the Monster this card is equipped to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch Tasuke Knight into Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's gonna attack him with her Phantom Butterfly Assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll only take 100 points of damage if you do attack him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Monster Effect of Phantom Butterfly Assassin Morph!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once per turn, when an opponent's Monster changes its Battle Position, she can decrease its Attack and Defense Power by 1000 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tasuke Knight's Attack Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Phantom Butterfly Assassin Morph to attack Tasuke Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Scale Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then activate the Monster Effect of Phantom Butterfly Assassin Swallowtail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Monster on the field inflicts Battle Damage other than this card,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one of my opponent's Monsters loses Attack Power equal to that damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now even Rai Rider's Attack Power was decreased!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then use Phantom Butterfly Assassin Swallowtail to attack Rai Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Limit Scale Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's only got 2400 Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he lost 1600 points in one go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you had more guts than this, but you turned out to be nothing but an incompetent Duelist with no spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line! You sure you should be so happy about such a small amount of damage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This match is just beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Rai Rider's Monster Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster who battles with this Monster can't battle during my opponent's next turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, and that's all your spirit can offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your field's completely empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ends on my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card face-down and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Black Mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Blade Bouncer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then Direct Attack with Hammer-Rush Bouncer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I control no Magic or Trap Cards when this card attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the opposing player can't activate any of their Magic and Trap Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, no matter what card you set, you can't use any of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why he hasn't set any cards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! If this attack goes through, Yuma-{\i1}kun{\i0} will be left with only 100 Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Hammer-Rush Bouncer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy Knuckle!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He was hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A spineless coward with nothing but talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need to do is finish you off with Blade Bouncer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! 1600 Life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Monster protected him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gagaga Gardna can be Special Summoned from my hand in Attack Mode when I receive a Direct Attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And by discarding a card from my hand, I can negate the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time Hammer-Rush Bouncer attacked directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he Special Summoned Gagaga Gardna to nullify the damage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and discarded a card from his hand to prevent Gagaga Gardna from being destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still take damage equal to the difference in the Monsters' Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gagaga Gardna has 1500 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack using the 1800 Attack Power Blade Bouncer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Straight Slash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I discard a card from my hand to activate Gagaga Gardna's Monster Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He takes another 300 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now the battle's over and I managed to protect Gagaga Gardna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Blade Bouncer's Monster Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By discarding a card from my hand, this Monster can attack once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got four cards in his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he manages to endure this attack, he can still attack four more times?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Blade Bouncer! Attack Gagaga Gardna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight Slash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gagaga Gardna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I discard a card from my hand to activate Gagaga Gardna's Monster Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now your hand is at zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of your spirit, you won't be able to use Gagaga Gardna's effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Blade Bouncer's Monster Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Blade Bouncer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Gagaga Bouncer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straight Slash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gagaga Gardna!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone gave me some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.47,0:22:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I was able to paint a rainbow with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.15,0:22:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to become someone perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.73,0:22:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even with me suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't seem to grasp victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:22:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to bloom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must be having some kind of weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But If I must fulfill this,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.46,0:23:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I don't mind being laughed at for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.42,0:23:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since it's because your limits are decided on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.64,0:23:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll show it, overcoming it to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, I'm aiming for the big blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.06,0:23:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For all of its glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.37,0:23:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All of those countless flower petals
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They came at the expense of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.87,0:23:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}me being able to reach those heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah, even though I lost my way today,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I still yearn for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Freesia of Desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.40,0:23:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been cornered in my Duel with Droite and Gauche while Astral's gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:23:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you off fighting somewhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel you bringing it to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.83,0:24:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose this Duel, Astral's gonna disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our bond!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.97,0:24:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.34,0:24:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Connect the Hope Together! Hope Sword Mars Slash!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.35,0:24:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, were you aware that mice sometimes crawl around your room late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.15,0:24:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?! I better call an exterminator!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? I've gathered up a bunch of talented Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.78,0:24:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I named them "Chuma"!\N (Chuu: The sound mice make)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.24,0:24:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I supposed to get along with them?!
